    \postersection{Network Visualizer}
    \hfill Chris Donahue

    {\bf Braincraft} comes bundled with a visualizer for the neural networks it produces. The tool allows the user to see, test and edit the networks that the library produced. An edited network can then be used by the library as a seed structure.\\

