  \postersection{Potential Applications}

    \begin{center}
    \begin{minipage}{0.80\linewidth}
    {\bf Braincraft} is a flexible library with a wide variety of potential uses. Because it is written in Java, Braincraft lends itself nicely to the development of software for the Android operating system. It is also being employed for experimentation with signal processing. A plugin is currently being developed to create audio filters and synthesizers using Braincraft and the Steinberg VST format.
    \end{minipage} \hfill%
    \begin{minipage}{0.19\linewidth}
